data.text: @itsyourdest But it went down as fast as it came and I’ve been mostly fine since, just felt a little off yesterday. Today I feel more like my self!

@itsyourdest Hey!! I also had a reaction, what was yours like? I’m not sure what to do about my second dose. I was good for 20 min after the shot, then I felt a massive rush feeling in my face and my heart rate went up to 147 after being 80ish the entire 30 minutes I was there.
